addBar

public void addBar(java.lang.String levelName,
                   java.lang.String imagePath,
                   java.awt.Insets insets,
                   int level)
Adds an additional level bar. The order of adding is relevant for painting - last added bar will be painted at last.

Parameters:
levelName - Name used as id for this level bar.
imagePath - Absolute resource path to the image used for painting background (first character is a slash).
insets - Insets of image (non stretchable region).
level - Value of the current level.
